page.title: 18WICKENTREE NURSERIES
page.content:
Wickentree nureries is run by Mr. Fox and covers 9 acres.
It is open each day between 8.00 a.m. to 8.00 p.m. and the busiest day for sales is Saturday.
He grows potatoes, carrots, swedes, leeks, onions, cabbage, cauliflower, runner beans and lettuces with potatoes being his most popular vegetable. He sells many shrubs with Leylandii being asked for most frequently. Fruit is very popular and includes raspberries, strawberries, gooseberries and tomatoes sold in season.
Christmas trees are also sold and are now more popular than ever.
